org.eclipse.scada.configuration.infrastructure

Interface EquinoxApplication

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MasterServer, ValueArchiveServer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EquinoxApplicationImpl, MasterServerImpl, ValueArchiveServerImpl

    public interface EquinoxApplication
    A representation of the model object 'Equinox Application'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Instance Number
    • Configurations

    See Also:
    InfrastructurePackage.getEquinoxApplication()
